{"tid":985947,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【華為危機】中國駐加大使再警告 加國禁華為5G設備將有「後果」","createTime":"2019-01-18T05:16:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T15:05:41.000Z","uid":125193,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a9a6c97d6f72fca8e9b55af87684d7232d8e7d34","tid":985947,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T05:16:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190118/59155642\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190118%2F59155642&d=QL8Dn08IhbOMzyUdcig6xf6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=2b7e080b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190118%2F59155642&h=dbe1aff0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190118/59155642</a><br />\n華為副董事長兼財務總監孟晚舟在加拿大被捕一案，令到中加關係緊張，中國駐加拿大大使盧沙野昨日舉行記者會，向加國發出警告，揚言如果加拿大禁止華為向加拿大5G網絡提供設備，「將會有後果」。他沒有說明會有甚麼「後果」，但強調「希望加拿大政府作出明智決定」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【華為危機】學術界爆恐慌 牛津大學暫停華為捐款<br />\n<br />\n當被記者追問加拿大禁止使用華為5G網絡設備將有何「後果」時，盧沙野說：「他不確定屆時會有甚麼事，不過他相信會有所影響」，他沒有透露具體內容。加拿大暫時未公佈禁止使用華為5G設備，加拿大外長方慧蘭（Chrystia Freeland）早前曾拒絕透露對5G技術的審查細節。"},{"pid":"2590d2e205dbb86cbdf0156af20659157feea7f1","tid":985947,"uid":125193,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T05:17:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6738XOV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6738XOV.png&h=c882e635&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"303e6631e11ea2942411b7490226d9e368f02879","tid":985947,"uid":37413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T06:19:16.000Z","msg":"累社會咁，好撚驚呀"},{"pid":"0024f44b1b9af1f1ef03cbb86f0aa9ff277cf690","tid":985947,"uid":99205,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2590d2e205dbb86cbdf0156af20659157feea7f1","tid":985947,"uid":125193,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T05:1